**Udacity**
Udacity is an online learning platform focused on tech skills like AI, data science, programming, and cloud computing, offering structured programs called Nanodegrees.
It emphasizes hands-on learning through real-world projects, mentorship, and industry-designed curriculum to make learners job-ready.
Founded in 2011, it now serves millions of learners globally and focuses more on career-oriented, practical education rather than traditional academic courses.

Link: https://www.udacity.com/

