**Up Work**
Upwork is a global freelancing platform that connects businesses with independent professionals for services like software development, data engineering, design, writing, and marketing.
It works as a digital marketplace where freelancers create profiles, apply to projects, set their rates, and get paid securely through built-in contracts and payment systems.
The platform is widely used for hiring remote talent, building freelance careers, outsourcing work, and scaling projects without needing full-time employees.

Link: https://www.upwork.com/

